Using ONLY the information provided in the briefs and background description below, generate a complete asset documentation entry for this background.

Do not add information that is not explicitly stated in the briefs or background description provided.

Location brief: [LOCATION_BRIEF]
Layout brief: [P04_OUTPUT]
Colour key brief: [P05_OUTPUT]
Background description: [BACKGROUND_DESCRIPTION]

Generate the asset documentation entry in the following structured format:

