## 🏢 Intended Workflow or Task

Step 1 of the review and handoff stage — runs once per background after P08 asset documentation is completed and approved.

- **Trigger:** Asset documentation completed (P08)
- **Actor:** QA reviewer / art director
- **Timing:** Before final approval
- **Next step:** Feeds into P10 (handoff preparation)
```
## Production chain:

P08 Asset Documentation → P09 Quality Review → Approval → Handoff (P10)
```

---

## ❗ Problem Being 

Without structured quality checks:

- errors are discovered late
- rework increases
- delivery delays occur

**Pain points addressed:**
- Inconsistent review standards
- Subjective approval decisions
- Lack of final validation

## ⚡ Automation Potential

**Level: Medium**

| Dimension | Assessment |
|-----------|------------|
| Repetitiveness | Triggered once per location per episode |
| Data availability | All inputs available from previous pipeline prompts P02–P08 |
| Human judgment needed | Supervisor resolves FAIL and UNABLE TO ASSESS items before final clearance |
| Integration possibility | PASS/FAIL output can feed directly into Shotgrid review status and handoff queue |
| Estimated time saving | ~70% — from 30–45 min to 10 min per background |

**Human-in-the-loop role:** Final approval must remain with art director.

---

## ⚠️ Risks and Limitations

| Risk | Level | Mitigation |
|------|-------|------------|
| Marks checklist items PASS based on documentation alone without physical file review | **High** | UNABLE TO ASSESS status built into output for all items requiring visual or physical file confirmation |
| Supervisor clears background for handoff without resolving UNABLE TO ASSESS items | **High** | Governance policy: CONDITIONAL PASS cannot be upgraded to PASS without physical file review sign-off on all UNABLE TO ASSESS items |
| Incomplete pipeline inputs produce incomplete quality review | **High** | Prompt grounding constraint limits review to provided inputs |
| Junior artist proceeds without art director review | **High** | Prompt grounding constraint limits review to provided inputs — missing inputs flagged as UNABLE TO ASSESS rather than assumed |

**Overall risk rating: HIGH** — Supervisor resolution of all FAIL and UNABLE TO ASSESS items through physical review is non-negotiable before background is cleared for handoff

